* 0.1.6    UNRELEASED


* 0.1.5    2025-04-04

+ Add examples for revisions and ranges (#106)
+ Change default values for parameters
  + Add SHA_LIMIT to misc parameters (#118)
  + Use a monospace font (#117)
+ Allow extra params for DAG nodes and edges (#114)
+ Remove option to mark commits (#113)
+ Customize subprocess.CalledProcessError (#108)

** Bugfixes

+ Fix rev_parse_descriptors and graphviz nodes sorting (#111)

* 0.1.4    2025-04-02

+ Remove the ls_remote parameter (#99)
+ Provide interface to add annotations to the DAG (#100)
+ Add git rebase --onto example (#98)
  + Change the -R cla to take a range expression (#97)
+ Add option to change config file name (#93)

** Bugfixes

+ Fix problem with tree connectivity visualization (#95)

* 0.1.3    2025-03-28

+ Store user-parameters in a configuration file (#4)
+ Add a new flag to show PRs heads (#86)
+ Add command-line flag to embed the SVG in HTML (#82, #81)

** Bugfixes

+ Verify repository path before processing (#87)
+ Fix stash creation in unit tests (#84)

* 0.1.2    2025-03-22

